plitting ensures no data leakage between train and test sets. SMOTE and class-weighted loss functions address the severe class imbalance, while leave-one-patient-out cross-validation tests generalization."}]]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"id":"status","className":"py-24","children":["$","$L3",null,{"children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-mono text-sm text-[var(--muted)]","children":"// status"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-[var(--fg)] mt-2","children":"Current Status"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-[var(--card)] border border-amber-500/20 rounded-xl p-6 mt-6","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-[var(--fg)]","children":"This project is actively being developed as part of Spring 2026 coursework at George Washington University. The data pipeline and feature extraction modules are complete; model training and evaluation are in progress."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-2 mt-4","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-green-400","children":"✅"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-[var(--fg)]","children":"Data pipeline & preprocessing"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-green-400","children":"✅"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-[var(--fg)]","children":"Feature extraction (5 methods)"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-amber-400","children":"🔄"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-[var(--fg)]","children":"Model training & hyperparameter tuning"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-[var(--muted)]","children":"⬜"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-[var(--muted)]","children":"Cross-patient evaluation"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm","children":[["$","